title: German 1 Online Course 3.0
description:
Learn to speak German correctly and with confidence saving time
and money. Learn to speak German online with LearnPlus: it&#039;s
easy, fun and effective. LearnPlus combines the advantages of
both computer-assisted and traditional classroom learning in one
effective tool. It allows you to study effectively at any time
and in any place and gives automatic and personal feedback on
your learning progress. You can actively use German from the
beginning thanks to a wide range of interactive features:
multimedia lessons and role-plays, learning games, and
state-of-the-art speech recognition exercises to name but a few.
